  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>DLC  <strong>Hazard of the Ages</strong>  also included: Fight historical diseases at their peak!<br><br>Face powerful bosses in a soulslike challenge amidst bullet hell! Each one will test your adaptability, skills, and strategic thinking, as you are fragile and will need to manage your stamina to dodge with your dash amidst intense, fast-paced action! To progress, you don't just need to defeat them but also master the combats to achieve the best rankings and obtain the stars needed to unlock more battles.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Customize your virus with genetic alterations: Want to be faster? More offensive? More resilient? The choice is yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2>25+ bosses based on real-world microscopic organisms.<br><br>Challenging boss battles with a strong focus on dodging and stamina management.<br><br>Extra game modes (Endless Roguelite, Arcade).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Exclusive soundtrack for each boss, energetic, with fusions of drum and bass and various other electronic music genres.<br><br>Multiple equipment options for head (your shots), legs (your dash), and body (passive abilities) that deeply alter the way you play.<br><br>15+ mini-virus allies with various functions for your battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready to dive into this microscopic adventure, but be careful not to be eradicated!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/fadefb39ad81bf8bb16efc80ea3d3b14.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>DLC  <strong>Hazard of the Ages</strong>  also included: Fight historical diseases at their peak!<br><br>Face powerful bosses in a soulslike challenge amidst bullet hell! Each one will test your adaptability, skills, and strategic thinking, as you are fragile and will need to manage your stamina to dodge with your dash amidst intense, fast-paced action! To progress, you don't just need to defeat them but also master the combats to achieve the best rankings and obtain the stars needed to unlock more battles.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/2f9dc8d8f0df75f87b1e2040e52cf5fd.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Customize your virus with genetic alterations: Want to be faster? More offensive? More resilient? The choice is yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2>25+ bosses based on real-world microscopic organisms.<br><br>Challenging boss battles with a strong focus on dodging and stamina management.<br><br>Extra game modes (Endless Roguelite, Arcade).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/13dfef8da21ef4d8ade89acfdfd1056e.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Exclusive soundtrack for each boss, energetic, with fusions of drum and bass and various other electronic music genres.<br><br>Multiple equipment options for head (your shots), legs (your dash), and body (passive abilities) that deeply alter the way you play.<br><br>15+ mini-virus allies with various functions for your battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.poster.avif?t=1759176351\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.webm?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059420/extras/1e6efb4e04c2898572979df1b1a94f88.mp4?t=1759176351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready to dive into this microscopic adventure, but be careful not to be eradicated!",
